title: Challenge and Growth
on-arrival: progress = 16

Facilyn: Now we will look where you find challenge and growth. What calls for your creativity, what do you find stimulating?

Facilyn: What kind of activity or work environment helps you become all you can be?

- #challenge_aspects

@qolcg_explanation
title: Please explain a bit further
max-visits: 1
tags: challenge_aspects

Me: Please explain a bit further.

Facilyn: Think about what energizes you and pushes you to grow. What sort of working environment stimulates resourcefulness and allows you to reach your full potential? Focus on what brings out your best.

Facilyn: Challenge and growth aren't about stress or difficulty for their own sake — they're about engaging your capabilities fully and expanding them.

A cleaning robot methodically works its way around the teahouse, pausing to contemplate a particularly stubborn tea stain with what appears to be genuine philosophical concern.

